ign:center\"|  ||style=\"text-align:left\"|\n|-\n| 2018 || 9\u201310 || 4\u20132 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|  ||style=\"text-align:center\"|  ||style=\"text-align:left\"|\n|-\n| 2019 || 10\u201311 || 4\u20135 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|  ||style=\"text-align:center\"|  ||style=\"text-align:left\"|\n|-\n| 2020 || 5\u20134 || 0\u20130 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|  ||style=\"text-align:center\"|  ||style=\"text-align:left\"| Season cancelled due to [[COVID-19]]\n|-\n| '''TOTALS''' || '''203\u2013148''' || '''55\u201336''' || || ||\n|}\n\n==Postseason Results==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year !! Round !! Opponent !! Result/Score\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 2004 || First Round || [[Clemson Tigers women's tennis|Clemson]] || L 0\u20134\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Troy Trojans|Tennis]]\n[[Category:College women's tennis teams in the United States]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox college tennis team\n| name = Troy Trojans women's tennis\n| logo = TroyUniversityTrojans-logo.gif\n| logo_size = 200\n| founded = \n| university = Troy University\n| athletic_director = Brent Jones\n| coach = Rawia Elsisi\n| tenure = 5th     <!-- First season was 2014 -->\n| conference = Sun Belt Conference\n| conference_short = SBC\n| division = \n| location =\n| city = Troy\n| state = Alabama\n| stateabb = AL\n| stadium = [[Jimmy Lunsford Tennis Complex]]\n| nickname = \n| color1 = \n| color2 = \n| color3 = \n| color4 = \n| colorfootnotes = \n| hex1 = \n| hex2 = \n| hex3 = \n| hex4 = \n| NCAAchampion = \n| NCAArunnerup = \n| NCAAsemifinals = \n| NCAAquarterfinals = \n| NCAAroundof16 = \n| NCAAroundof32 = \n| NCAAtourneys = 2004\n| conference_tournament = 1995, 2004\n| conference_season = \n}}\n\nThe '''Troy Trojans women's tennis''' team represents [[Troy University]] and plays in the [[Sun Belt Conference]].  All home matches are played at the 12-court [[Jimmy Lunsford Tennis Complex]] on Troy's campus.\n\n==History==\nThe women's tennis team began playing in the 1980s, and becau